4. âœ… Support for product types (case classes, tuples)
5. âœ… Support for sum types (sealed traits, enums) in Scala 3 only
6. âœ… Normalized type name generation
7. âœ… `Selectable` bindings (Scala 3) and `Dynamic` bindings (Scala 2)
8. âœ… Integration with `Into`/`As` for structural â†” nominal conversions
9. âœ… Comprehensive test suite (300+ test cases)
10. âœ… Clear error messages for unsupported cases
11. âœ… Documentation with examples

